SETUP NOTES

SERVER REQUIREMENTS (LAMP stack)
Fedora 15+ with the default following apps: php 5.3+, mysql 5.5+, apache 2.2+
OR
Fedora 15+ with the default following apps: php-fpm 5.3+, mysql 5.5+, nginx 1+

openssh-clients e2fsprogs sysstat ruby rsync

httpd php OR nginx php-fpm
mysql-server memcached
php-cli php-xml php-gd php-pdo php-mysql php-mbstring
php-pecl-memcache php-pecl-apc

CODE
- svn co code
- svn co toolkit/Zend_1_11_11 /Minify /ZFDebug /SmartSprite into toolkit folder
- Create virtual host
- update application.ini (for database, memcache configs)

FINE TUNNING
find apache/nginx config in the compassites/scripts/apache/  or nginx folder


DATABASE (find sql in the compassites/scripts/database/ folder)
- create main database


svn co http://svn.lan/compassites/trunk compassites
svn co svn+ssh://svn.lan/compassites/branches/version2 compassites
